import React from 'react';

const FacebookIcon = () => (

			<g id="Reliant-Homepage-Form-Expanded" transform="translate(-536.000000, -164.000000)">
				<g id="Group-15" transform="translate(536.000000, 164.000000)">
					<ellipse id="Oval" fill="#FFFFFF" cx="13.5" cy="13" rx="13.5" ry="13"></ellipse>
					<g id="Group-4" transform="translate(14.000000, 13.000000) rotate(-360.000000) translate(-14.000000, -13.000000) translate(8.000000, 7.000000)" fill="#005EFF">
						<polygon id="Rectangle" transform="translate(6.000000, 6.000000) rotate(45.000000) translate(-6.000000, -6.000000) " points="-1.2 4.8 13.2 4.8 13.2 7.2 -1.2 7.2"></polygon>
						<polygon id="Rectangle" transform="translate(6.000000, 6.000000) scale(-1, 1) rotate(45.000000) translate(-6.000000, -6.000000) " points="-1.2 4.8 13.2 4.8 13.2 7.2 -1.2 7.2"></polygon>

);

export default FacebookIcon;
